   "source": [
    "## 🧠 Learning Happens Here\n",
    "\n",
    "Synaptic weights change during learning using rules like:\n",
    "\n",
    "Hebbian Learning\n",
    "\n",
    "Spike-Timing Dependent Plasticity\n",
    "\n",
    "These rules adjust weights based on spike timing.\n",
    "\n",
    "This explains how SNNs learn without backpropagation."
   ]
